website that shows post that has many tags.
when clicked on tags will show the post tagged to that tag

index-
shows x amount of posts order by created_at

post - title, blog, posts_tags_id, timestamps
tag - name, posts_tags_id, timestamps
posts_tags - post_id, tag_id, timestamps

